{
"#name"
:
{
"agent"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"x-cmd AI Agent 集成工具"
,
"en"
:
"x-cmd AI Agent integration tool"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x agent <subcmd>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"集成 x-cmd 到 Claude、Codex、Opencode、Kimi 等 AI 工具，管理 ~/AGENTS.md 及配置文件"
,
"en"
:
"Integrate x-cmd into Claude, Codex, Opencode, Kimi and other AI tools, manage ~/AGENTS.md and configs"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"除了使用 x agent setup，还可以手动引入如下提示词到你的 AGENT 文件中。\nLoad x-cmd with `. ~/.x-cmd.root/X` (required before using `x`), then `x -h` for help. Docs: https://x-cmd.com/llms.txt\n"
,
"en"
:
"Besides using x agent setup, you can also manually add the following prompt to your AGENT file.\nLoad x-cmd with `. ~/.x-cmd.root/X` (required before using `x`), then `x -h` for help. Docs: https://x-cmd.com/llms.txt\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"Harness: AI 工具接口（kimi-cli、claude、codex、gemini-cli、opencode）\nAgent 000/001: 两个独立的 AI Agent 配置身份\n"
,
"en"
:
"Harness: AI tool interface (kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode)\nAgent 000/001: Two independent AI Agent configuration identities\n"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Config"
:
[
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
,
"init"
]
,
"#subcmd:Setup"
:
[
"setup"
,
"unify"
]
,
"setup"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"让主流 AI 工具使用 x-cmd 提示词和技能"
,
"en"
:
"Enable mainstream AI tools to use x-cmd prompts and skills"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"1. 创建 ~/AGENTS.md（如果不存在）\n2. 安装 x-cmd skills 到 ~/.agents、~/.claude、~/.codex、~/.gemini、~/.config/opencode\n"
,
"en"
:
"1. Create ~/AGENTS.md (if not exists)\n2. Install x-cmd skills to ~/.agents, ~/.claude, ~/.codex, ~/.gemini, ~/.config/opencode\n"
}
]
}
,
"unify"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"合并各 AI 工具配置文件到 ~/AGENTS.md 并创建 symlink"
,
"en"
:
"Merge AI tool config files into ~/AGENTS.md and create symlinks"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Processes config files:\n1. Merge ~/CLAUDE.md, ~/.gemini/GEMINI.md, ~/.codex/AGENTS.md,\n   ~/.config/opencode/AGENTS.md into ~/AGENTS.md\n2. Delete originals, create symlinks to ~/AGENTS.md\n3. Identical content files are replaced directly without merging\n"
,
"cn"
:
"处理各 AI 工具配置文件：\n1. 将 ~/CLAUDE.md、~/.gemini/GEMINI.md、~/.codex/AGENTS.md、\n   ~/.config/opencode/AGENTS.md 的内容合并到 ~/AGENTS.md\n2. 删除原文件，创建指向 ~/AGENTS.md 的 symlink\n3. 内容相同的文件直接替换为 symlink，无需合并\n"
}
]
}
,
"#subcmd:Request"
:
[
"request"
]
,
"request"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"向 AI harness 发送请求"
,
"en"
:
"Send request to AI harness"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Without --harness, uses configured default from --cfg or --cur\n--file can be used multiple times to attach multiple files\n"
,
"cn"
:
"不指定 --harness 时使用 --cfg 或 --cur 配置的默认值\n--file 可多次使用以附加多个文件\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x agent request --harness <harness> --file <file> --output <file> <prompt>"
:
null
}
]
,
"--harness"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定 AI 工具接口"
,
"en"
:
"Specify AI tool interface"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#cand"
:
[
"kimi-cli"
,
"claude"
,
"codex"
,
"gemini-cli"
,
"opencode"
]
}
}
,
"--file"
:
{
"#multiple"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"附加到提示词的文件"
,
"en"
:
"File to attach to prompt"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"--output"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出文件路径"
,
"en"
:
"Output file path"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"#n"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"提示词内容"
,
"en"
:
"Prompt content"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request \"Explain this code\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 使用默认 harness 发送请求"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Send request using default harness"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request --harness claude --file main.py \"Review this code\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定 harness 并附加文件发送请求"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Send request with specific harness and attached file"
}
]
}
,
"--cfg"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"持久化配置（保存到配置文件，跨会话生效）"
,
"en"
:
"Persistent configuration (saved to config file, cross-session)"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"zero_harness: Default AI tool for Agent 000\none_harness: Default AI tool for Agent 001\nAvailable: kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode\n"
,
"cn"
:
"zero_harness: Agent 000 默认 AI 工具\none_harness: Agent 001 默认 AI 工具\n可选: kimi-cli, claude, codex, gemini-cli, opencode\n"
}
]
,
"clear"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"清除所有已保存的配置（恢复默认值）"
,
"en"
:
"Clear all saved configuration (restore defaults)"
}
}
,
"cat"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示当前配置值"
,
"en"
:
"Display current configuration values"
}
}
,
"#n"
:
{
"#cand"
:
[
{
"zero_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Agent 000 的默认 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Default harness for Agent 000"
}
}
}
,
{
"one_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Agent 001 的默认 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Default harness for Agent 001"
}
}
}
]
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cfg zero_harness=kimi-cli one_harness=claude"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 同时设置两个 Agent 的默认 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Set default harness for both Agents"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cfg cat"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看当前保存的配置"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View current saved configuration"
}
]
}
,
"--cur"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"临时配置（仅当前 shell 会话生效）"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary configuration (current shell session only)"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"zero_harness: Temporary AI tool for Agent 000\none_harness: Temporary AI tool for Agent 001\nOverrides --cfg for current session only\n"
,
"cn"
:
"zero_harness: Agent 000 临时 AI 工具\none_harness: Agent 001 临时 AI 工具\n仅覆盖当前会话的 --cfg 配置\n"
}
]
,
"set"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"设置临时配置值"
,
"en"
:
"Set temporary configuration values"
}
,
"zero_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Agent 000 临时 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary harness for Agent 000"
}
}
,
"one_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Agent 001 临时 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary harness for Agent 001"
}
}
,
"#n"
:
{
"#cand"
:
[
{
"zero_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Agent 000 临时 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary harness for Agent 000"
}
}
}
,
{
"one_harness="
:
{
"#nospace"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Agent 001 临时 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Temporary harness for Agent 001"
}
}
}
]
}
}
}
,
"init"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"交互式初始化配置（选择并设置 zero_harness、one_harness）"
,
"en"
:
"Interactive initialization (select and set zero_harness, one_harness)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent setup"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 配置 AI 工具使用 x-cmd"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Configure AI tools to use x-cmd"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent init"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 交互式选择 AI 工具"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Interactively select AI tools"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cfg zero_harness=kimi-cli one_harness=claude"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 设置两个 Agent 的默认 harness"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Set default harness for both Agents"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cfg cat"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看已保存的配置"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View saved configuration"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cfg clear"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 清除所有配置恢复默认"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Clear all configuration to defaults"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent --cur set zero_harness=kimi-cli"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 临时设置（仅当前会话）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Set temporarily (current session only)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent unify"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 合并各 AI 工具配置文件"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Merge config files from AI tools"
}
]
,
"#other"
:
{
"en"
:
{
"Please visit our homepage for more information:"
:
"https://x-cmd.com"
}
,
"cn"
:
{
"请访问我们的主页以获取更多信息："
:
